<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/GroupPrograms.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/home_style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="group-programs-header">
        <h1>Group Programs</h1>
        <p>Join our exciting group programs and train with others!</p>
    </div>

    <section class="group-programs-info container my-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4 mb-md-0">
                <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/img/group-workouts-1-1-1024x536.jpg")" alt="Group Programs"
                     class="img-fluid rounded"
                     style="max-height: 400px; object-fit: cover; width: 100%;">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <h2>What We Offer</h2>
                <p>Our group programs are designed for all fitness levels. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced athlete, we have something for you. Join a group and get motivated by working out with others!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="group-programs-benefits">
        <h2>Benefits of Group Programs</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Motivation from peers</li>
            <li>Variety in workouts</li>
            <li>Affordable pricing</li>
            <li>Fun and engaging environment</li>
            <li>Expert guidance from certified trainers</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="group-programs-cta">
        <p>Ready to start your fitness transformation?</p>
        <a href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")" class="btn-cta">Contact Us to Book Your Session</a>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>